@startuml Encrypter_CRC

title Encrypter — CRC Diagram

class Encrypter {
  == Responsibilities ==
  Initialize and hold the AES-256 secret key
  Encrypt a plaintext message string using AESHelper
  Decrypt a ciphertext message string using AESHelper
  Provide encrypt / decrypt operations to Sender and Receiver
  --
  == Collaborators ==
  AESHelper
}

class AESHelper {
  (collaborator)
}

Encrypter --> AESHelper : setKey(), encrypt(), decrypt() >

@enduml
